//- Hero
gz-hero

//- Welcome banner
gz-welcome-banner

//- Content
div.r2s-content

  md-content(layout-padding, layout='row', layout-wrap, layout-xs='column')

    //- Active kids
    div(flex-xs, flex-sm='100', flex-gt-sm='33', layout='column')
      md-card(layout='row', layout-wrap)
        div(flex-gt-sm='100', flex-xs='100', flex-sm='50', flex-order-sm='2', flex-order-gt-sm='1')
          img.md-card-image(
            width='100%',
            ng-src='/images/active_kids.svg',
            alt='Illustration of a child on a scooter, one on a bicycle, and one walking'
          )
        div(flex-gt-sm='100', flex-sm='50', flex-order-sm='1', flex-order-gt-sm='2')
          md-card-title
            md-card-title-text.md-headline
              | More fun
          md-card-content
            p
              | Kids love to move and have fun, but research shows they are not
              |  getting enough of their daily dose. By walking, scooting or
              |  cycling to school kids:
            md-list.md-dense
              //- md-list-item(ng-click='vm.blah()')
              md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('active_a')")
                md-icon.material-icons done
                .md-list-item-text
                  p Build stronger bodies and bones
              md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('active_b')")
                md-icon.material-icons done
                .md-list-item-text
                  p Feel more relaxed and confident
              md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('active_c')")
                md-icon.material-icons done
                .md-list-item-text
                  p Have more fun on the way to school, and in class

    //- Cars
    div(flex, flex-sm='50', flex-gt-sm='33', layout='column')
      md-card
        img.md-card-image(
          ng-src='/images/less_cars.svg',
          alt='Illustration of less cars'
        )
        md-card-title
          md-card-title-text.md-headline
            | Less cars
        md-card-content
          p
            | Australian children are among the most chauffeured young people
            |  in the world. Less cars around our schools
            |  means:
          md-list.md-dense
            md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('cars_a')")
              md-icon.material-icons done
              .md-list-item-text
                p Less traffic in our communities
            md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('cars_a')")
              md-icon.material-icons done
              .md-list-item-text
                p Less pollution across our cities
            md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('cars_a')")
              md-icon.material-icons done
              .md-list-item-text
                p A happier, healhier world
    //- Trees
    div(flex, flex-sm='50', flex-gt-sm='33', layout='column')
      md-card
        img.md-card-image(
          ng-src='/images/more_trees.svg',
          alt='Illustration of trees'
        )
        md-card-title
          md-card-title-text.md-headline
            | More trees
        md-card-content
          p
            | For every step you and your school take towards more active
            |  travellers we will plant a tree to supercharge your
            |  efforts. More trees means:
          md-list.md-dense
            md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('trees_a')")
              md-icon.material-icons done
              .md-list-item-text
                p More carbon filtered from the air
            md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('trees_a')")
              md-icon.material-icons done
              .md-list-item-text
                p More habitat for our animals
            md-list-item(ng-click="vm.about('trees_a')")
              md-icon.material-icons done
              .md-list-item-text
                p More trees for us to climb
